<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ق ت ت:</span> <span class="c2">(الْقَتُّ)</span> نَمُّ الْحَدِيثِ وَبَابُهُ رَدَّ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> «لَا يَدْخُلُ الْجَنَّةَ <span class="c2">(قَتَّاتٌ)</span> » . وَ <span class="c2">(الْقَتُّ)</span> الْفِصْفَصَةُ الْوَاحِدَةُ <span class="c2">(قَتَّةٌ)</span> كَتَمْرَةٍ وَتَمْرٍ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>